{"tid":1746920,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屌你老母，一落街就有民賤聯派掌心雷","createTime":"2019-11-23T03:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:47:50.000Z","uid":94771,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"23e22ba6ada8671e739a8f783ed27bec3c708466","tid":1746920,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大大張１號票加個 ✓的單張，有收個就明講咩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你真係好難怪點解建制咁容易種票，同昆９人投佢票<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人地公關，宣傳做得好個依邊多多聲</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n事實係最關心選擇的人反而無出盡全力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地又同老人家傾計，又派掌心雷單張。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我落街貼個幾將不投建制派，唔夠半日就比人撕佐</strong>"},{"pid":"36f005c683f83c42a9fc029a0ed54c572d08d280","tid":1746920,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"事實係最關心<ins>選<del>舉</del></ins>的人反而無出盡全力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我落街貼個幾<ins><ins>張</ins></ins>不投建制派，唔夠半日就比人撕佐</strong>"},{"pid":"ae484f32ed85d06a392b0e7446f58677ce47cf2c","tid":1746920,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a155c9b1d8a772583f11ae865990c0d2848986bc","tid":1746920,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:48:18.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746369</a>"},{"pid":"be5affdca506d46e53cefc0fe569e9f43e54dcd2","tid":1746920,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc6bdca072f5fb7e0035dd0024a09999c80eef2","tid":1746920,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r